  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The soft robotic system could provide objective and quantifiable measures of subject
      performance. By combining voluntary motor intention and the robotic hand technology, the
      system will facilitate the recovery process of stroke patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
